query:

  `title`,
  `city`,
  `description`,
  `rules`,
  `capacity`,
  `userRole`,
  `locationText`,
  `locationRevealAt`,
  `eventDate`,
  `eventStatus`,
  `publishedAt`
) VALUES (
  'THE MIDNIGHT SESSION',
  'Jakarta',
  'An intimate gathering for the marked. Live music, exclusive previews, and conversations that stay inside. Dress code: Black.',
  'No phones during main event. What happens here stays here. Respect the space and each other.',
  50,
  'marked_initiate',
  'Location revealed 24 hours before the event. Check back closer to the date.',
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 6 DAY),
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY),
  'published',
  NOW()
);
